			<p>Leaks about both the game and the VR headset would generate massive speculation and excitement. People would likely discuss the potential capabilities of the VR technology, the game's features, and the overall immersive experience. Some might question the realism of the leaks. But these leaks and rumors will only excite the gaming community and technology enthusiasts. The general public would not react much to the leaks.</p>

